title: Terraria v1.3.0.4-GOG
description:
Terraria v1.3.0.4 (c) Re-Logic

Release Date : 07/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure
Languages : EN/FR/DE/IT/ES

Dig, Fight, Explore, Build: The very world is at your fingertips as
you fight for survival, fortune, and glory. Will you delve deep
into cavernous expanses in search of treasure and raw materials
with which to craft ever-evolving gear, machinery, and aesthetics?
Perhaps you will choose instead to seek out ever-greater foes to
test your mettle in combat? Maybe you will decide to construct your
own city to house the host of mysterious allies you may encounter
along your travels?
